- val(j,i): integer value of s[j..i-1] (leading zeros allowed)
- transition: dp[i][t] = max_{j ∈ [t-1..i-1]} dp[j][t-1] + val(j,i)
- reconstruction: track prev to recover split indices
- complexity: O(n²k) time, O(nk) space; use BigInt for large results

## Code Example
